{"tid":970641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣人：香港粥 ≠ 廣東粥","createTime":"2019-01-06T04:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T23:59:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ec67a10668a1e96ae32febda3d29c493bdd2ef95","tid":970641,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:12:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://jj5colorkitchen.pixnet.net/blog/post/303473292-香港粥-&ne;-廣東粥%21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjj5colorkitchen.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F303473292-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%B2%A5-%E2%89%A0-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1%E7%B2%A5%2521&d=ao9E%2F6OdHCl1a577d6iu3f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c03f5fea\" target=\"_blank\">http://jj5colorkitchen.pixnet.net/blog/post/303473292-香港粥-&ne;-廣東粥%21</a><br />\n<br />\n香港找不到台灣的「廣東粥」，正如四川找不到台灣的「紅燒牛肉麵」一樣。<br />\n<br />\n香港粥 &ne; 廣東粥!<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jj5colorkitchen/1443525861-3444865574.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjj5colorkitchen%2F1443525861-3444865574.jpg&h=4c2a2e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次回香港，總會留一餐吃粥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jj5colorkitchen/1443527977-4008724675_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjj5colorkitchen%2F1443527977-4008724675_n.jpg&h=dedec348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳統香港粥店分兩類，一類以早餐為主，簡單粥品配著腸粉炒麵油條吃，像台灣的豆漿配蛋餅燒餅包子一樣。<br />\n<br />\n另一種主攻午到晚餐的「生滾粥」。隨著香港租金日益高昂，現在大多從早餐賣到宵夜，賺到租金也希望賺到薪水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jj5colorkitchen/1443525881-1877573214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjj5colorkitchen%2F1443525881-1877573214.jpg&h=ee2aed11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖：香港一家老字號粥店(大坑京街康記粥店)拍下的手寫掛牆餐單。<br />\n<br />\n餐單上第一排的「生滾粥」，做法是先做好大鍋白粥底，然後用一小鍋撈起一人份的粥，放入「生」的材料，與粥一起在火上燒「滾」至熟，食材的鮮味直接溶入綿滑的「粥」內。這類功多的粥，香港人是午餐或晚餐才會點的，料多，一碗便吃飽。<br />\n<br />\n下左圖小鍋煮生滾粥的方法，也是台灣廣東粥的手法，但材料則大不同。香港的通常只有1-2種材料，切成大塊去煮，一邊大口吃料，一邊吃粥，注重單一材料的鮮味。台灣廣東粥強調料多，少則4-5樣，多的到連鎖店一碗粥內有十幾種料，海產、豬肉、蔬菜、蛋類全集在一起，要多熱鬧有多熱鬧！這種多料的台灣特式「廣東粥」，香港是找不到的啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jj5colorkitchen/1443525847-2750984032_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjj5colorkitchen%2F1443525847-2750984032_l.jpg&h=9ef832ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(圖片來源：香港蘋果日報。右圖來源：香港東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n「生滾粥」材料有幾大類，最普遍的是豬內臟（豬肝、豬腰、豬肚、粉腸）粥品，可單選一項內臟，也可點綜合的豬內臟粥~及第粥。有人叫「狀元及第粥」，有人叫「三元及第粥」，又大器又豪華，吃著覺得自己快升官了！其實，及第只是「雜底」(指豬下水)的廣東諧音而已！！<br />\n<br />\n「窩蛋」牛肉粥是指牛肉粥煮好後再打個生蛋在粥上，上桌時雞蛋需保持完整形狀，上右圖則是窩蛋及第粥，跟台灣廣東粥把蛋攪散也不同。<br />\n<br />\n我問愛到香港旅遊的朋友，最難忘，想一吃再吃的美食是什麼？很訝異的，很多回答「粥」！<br />\n<br />\n朋友說的粥，是最五花八門的生滾海鮮粥。 平民小吃店只供應淡水魚的魚片、魚肚肉；有規模的粥店從海魚、蝦球、帶子都有；酒樓餐廳甚至有石班、龍蝦、螃蟹、鮑魚等！海鮮熟成過程中釋放出來的鮮甜味，通通吸進粥裡！！粥有多甜多美味可想而知！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/jj5colorkitchen/1443525863-2477906987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjj5colorkitchen%2F1443525863-2477906987.jpg&h=32679eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皮蛋魚腩粥，我最愛的生滾粥。鯇魚腩沾上薑絲蔥花醬油，鮮！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣廣東粥<br />\n<a href=\"http://home.so-net.net.tw/ywc580510/dm1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhome.so-net.net.tw%2Fywc580510%2Fdm1.html&d=ao9E%2F6OdHCl1a577d6iu3f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d30af139\" target=\"_blank\">http://home.so-net.net.tw/ywc580510/dm1.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://home.so-net.net.tw/ywc580510/images/img_01_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhome.so-net.net.tw%2Fywc580510%2Fimages%2Fimg_01_04.jpg&h=0cd59a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/joelin1234/1327564508-144630466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fjoelin1234%2F1327564508-144630466.jpg&h=a855443b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/ksdelicacy/1391480002-3872142039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fksdelicacy%2F1391480002-3872142039.jpg&h=a6fc7fd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27f61b90d60ee9c2cad1035e04f40336b2da0f30","tid":970641,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"海南、上海同福建都影響到香港文化"},{"pid":"4f0a11fac5822c5ce4bc28b64490dc7a0e5cc116","tid":970641,"uid":162539,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"吖屌俾佢講到好肚餓"},{"pid":"072d1f77a707d9a43598c1efa577f7c73d14fefe","tid":970641,"uid":182499,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"突然好想食粥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4fc32dc08b1d463c768bd5013c08bb7bb72d70","tid":970641,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f3ae14c8b6ff31ca4bf61b98363f3d9e934f1f","tid":970641,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"臺灣人應學會香港地道一乾三濕食麵習俗"},{"pid":"493fc91bff4a1ecad93cba3d7d7da5ab8a560c6c","tid":970641,"uid":50310,"like":9,"dislike":15,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"其實生滾粥，得個快字<br />\n某程度上，浪費食材<br />\n<br />\n好的黃沙豬潤粥<br />\n需要煲成粒鐘，才可以令整碗粥都有淡淡的黃沙<br />\n<br />\n若然唔係想食到起沙的效果<br />\n深水埗維記豬潤麵唔會咁旺場<br />\n<br />\n對於未食過的人，唔會明白差異有幾遠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946970b44008f2955122b029d2e80dcb31df167b","tid":970641,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493fc91bff4a1ecad93cba3d7d7da5ab8a560c6c","tid":970641,"uid":50310,"like":9,"dislike":15,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"其實生滾粥，得個快字<br />\n某程度上，浪費食材<br />\n<br />\n好的黃沙豬潤粥<br />\n需要煲成粒鐘，才可以令整碗粥都有淡淡的黃沙<br />\n<br />\n若然唔係想食到起沙的效果<br />\n深水埗維記豬潤麵唔會咁旺場<br />\n<br />\n對於未食過的人，唔會明白差異有幾遠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"生滖粥 = 