ke":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實生滾粥，得個快字<br />\n某程度上，浪費食材<br />\n<br />\n好的黃沙豬潤粥<br />\n需要煲成粒鐘，才可以令整碗粥都有淡淡的黃沙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">若然唔係想食到起沙的效果<br />\n深水埗維記豬潤麵唔會咁旺場</span><br />\n<br />\n對於未食過的人，唔會明白差異有幾遠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>生滖粥 = 車仔面<br />\n放D料入去白粥<br />\n<br />\n真正煲叫老母煲啦<br />\n出面好少咁做</blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2FEXrJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2FEXrJ.jpg&h=5c588314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係正的黃沙豬潤粥<br />\n係充分感受到啲粥和豬潤溶合埋一齊<br />\n這才稱得上風味<br />\n<br />\n不過，不是香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Xn2CHXY1m8Q/Vuu9oeOxkII/AAAAAAAIiLE/0jTDOUWa4bMpmpI5sZEr6wl1cwlSm5xSg/s1600/10872362_10152509269021835_972546700_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Xn2CHXY1m8Q%2FVuu9oeOxkII%2FAAAAAAAIiLE%2F0jTDOUWa4bMpmpI5sZEr6wl1cwlSm5xSg%2Fs1600%2F10872362_10152509269021835_972546700_n.jpg&h=f920cf92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打你講笑咋吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n維記兜嘢啲豬膶點樣充分同啲湯融合埋一齊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n融合咗既只係浮係面嗰啲發粉泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64f8394086f18ba96433be73f490bd942a5e426","tid":970641,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"從來唔食粥 窮人先食粥"},{"pid":"722ea04b9b504a3cd3dc5fad5ba1ed3200ca17dd","tid":970641,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64f8394086f18ba96433be73f490bd942a5e426","tid":970641,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"從來唔食粥 窮人先食粥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"而家一碗粥都唔平啦<img s